         <div class="module mod-box  deepest"> 
          <h3 class="module-title"><span class="color">Chairman's</span> Message</h3> 
          <p>Mankind is the most gracious and precious gift of God created with a view to representing Him in this world.</p> 
          <p><a class="button-more" href="/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=31">read more</a></p> 
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-box width33 grid-h">
         <div class="module mod-box  deepest"> 
          <h3 class="module-title"><span class="color">VC's</span> Message</h3> 
          <p>The long standing tradition of our noble soil is to search and harness knowledge, and apply it for the well-being of society as a whole.</p> 
          <p><a class="button-more" href="/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=32">read more</a></p> 
         </div>
        </div>
