          <h3 class="module-title"><span class="color">Pro-VC's</span> Message</h3> 
          <p>The UITS has now earned its fame as the first IT based private university of Bangladesh.</p> 
          <p><a class="button-more" href="/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=33">read more</a></p> 
